Pasukan!

1001
01:49:22,971 --> 01:49:23,972
Serbu!

1002
01:51:26,677 --> 01:51:28,096
Kau makin kuat saja!

1003
01:51:28,179 --> 01:51:31,057
Jangan remehkan Yahiko
Myojin, samurai dari Tokyo, ini!

1004
01:51:38,189 --> 01:51:40,483
Bakar!

1005
01:51:40,566 --> 01:51:42,902
Kami sudah tahu rencana kalian!

1006
01:51:57,166 --> 01:52:01,421
Astaga, meriah sekali sambutannya
walau sudah malam begini!

1007
01:52:02,296 --> 01:52:06,634
