kalau Misao berjuang mencarimu?

1016
01:53:16,162 --> 01:53:20,791
Dia masih percaya kalau kau
tetap baik seperti yang dia ingat.

1017
01:53:20,875 --> 01:53:22,502
Itu bukan urusanku.

1018
01:53:23,544 --> 01:53:24,545
Dia adalah…

1019
01:53:26,088 --> 01:53:28,174
tamu penting di Aoiya ini.

1020
01:53:31,594 --> 01:53:34,347
Bersembunyi di
tengah keramaian, ya?

1021
01:53:34,430 --> 01:53:37,892
Sadarlah, Aoshi.

1022
01:53:39,602 --> 01:53:42,271
Yang kau butuhkan
bukan pertarungan,

1023
