1033
01:56:26,185 --> 01:56:27,937
Kebakaran! Segera padamkan!

1034
01:56:34,193 --> 01:56:35,486
Serahkan ini kepada kami.

1035
01:56:36,320 --> 01:56:37,196
Baiklah.

1036
01:56:42,493 --> 01:56:43,452
Diam sebentar.

