1050
02:00:13,370 --> 02:00:14,205
Jangan ke sini!

1051
02:00:35,351 --> 02:00:36,685
Aoshi…

1052
02:00:41,315 --> 02:00:42,316
Sudah serendah inikah…

1053
02:00:43,901 --> 02:00:47,738
kau sekarang?

1054
02:01:28,195 --> 02:01:30,489
Aku bukanlah Aoshi
yang kau kenal dulu.

1055
02:02:28,839 --> 02:02:29,673
Hei!

1056
02:02:31,550 --> 02:02:35,054
Ikan teri seperti kalian
tidak usah mengganggu!

1057
02:02:45,564 --> 02:02:46,607
Sano?

1058
02:02:47,399 --> 02:02:48,525
Kenapa kau ada di sini?

1059
02:02:52,446 --> 02:02:53,655
"Kenapa"?

1060
02:02:54,615 --> 02:02:57,326
Tentu saja untuk membantumu!

1061
02:03:04,249 --> 02:03:05,334
Terima kasih.

1062
02:03:11,882 --> 02:03:12,966
Sama-sama.

1063
02:03:13,842 --> 02:03:16,637
Kita menang!

1064
02:03:16,720 --> 02:03:17,971
Siapa mereka?

1065
02:03:19,640 --> 02:03:20,849
Tangkap mereka!

1066
02:03:23,102 --> 02:03:24,103
Himura.

1067
02:03:24,686 --> 02:03:25,521
Kau di sini juga?

1068
02:03:26,063 --> 02:03:27,564
Apa kau tidak merasa aneh?

1069
02:03:28,232 --> 02:03:29,108
Ya.

1070
02:03:29,900 --> 02:03:32,361
Di mana Shishio
dan Juppongatana?

1071
02:03:32,444 --> 02:03:35,280
Kenapa kalian terlihat suram?

1072
02:03:35,364 --> 02:03:38,033
Ini terlalu sederhana.

1073
02:03:39,451 --> 02:03:41,453
Jika Shishio ingin
membakar Kyoto,

1074
02:03:42,371 --> 02:03:44,790
dia pasti ingin
melihatnya langsung.

1075
02:04:09,565 --> 02:04:11,233
Nona Kaoru Kamiya?

1076
02:04:13,277 --> 02:04:14,528
Siapa kau?

1077
02:04:16,947 --> 02:04:18,240
Maksudmu,

1078
02:04:18,323 --> 02:04:20,617
